  <p class="mb-4">
    FXIFY Futures offers two optional upgrades at checkout to give you more flexibility and maximize your earnings:
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Profit Split Increase <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">(+10% of account price)</span></p>
      <p>Boosts your share by 10%, raising Starter accounts from 80% to 90% and Expert accounts from 90% to 100%.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Remove Daily Drawdown <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">(+10% of account price &mdash; Expert only)</span></p>
      <p>Removes the daily drawdown restriction, allowing for more trading flexibility. Only available on Expert accounts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Trading Rules ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trading Rules</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    FXIFY Futures gives you the freedom to trade futures on your own terms, but you'll need to follow a few key rules to keep your account active and eligible for payouts.
  </p>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-8">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
